&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;Walden Security is currently offering a sign on bonus of $2000 paid after 90 days on the contract. They are recruiting experienced Court Security Officers. CSOs will provide armed security to courthouses under the USMS contract.&lt;/div&gt;
